description: A two-minute silence marks the 75th anniversary of the end of World War Two in Europe.
title: VE Day: Isle of Man pauses to mark 75th anniversary
title_page: VE Day: Isle of Man pauses to mark 75th anniversary - BBC News
maintext: "Those countries of western Europe which were liberated from tyranny... stand deeply indebted to the people of that generation... as indeed do we, who came afterwards and who have been able to live our lives in peace."
